<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/><sp/>To<sp/>perform<sp/>multi-threaded<sp/>compilation<sp/>pass<sp/>-j.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">To<sp/>build<sp/>on<sp/>Windows:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/><sp/>Execute<sp/>./Scripts/rundockerbuild.ps1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/><sp/>The<sp/>script<sp/>will<sp/>pull<sp/>the<sp/>NWNX<sp/>Linux<sp/>Docker<sp/>builder<sp/>image</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Container<sp/>will<sp/>execute<sp/>the<sp/>./scripts/buildnwnx.sh<sp/>script</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/><sp/>To<sp/>perform<sp/>a<sp/>clean<sp/>build<sp/>pass<sp/>-FORCECLEAN<sp/>eg<sp/>&apos;./scripts/rundockerbuild.ps1<sp/>-FORCECLEAN&apos;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Contributing<sp/>code</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">All<sp/>contribution<sp/>are<sp/>welcome.<sp/>The<sp/>only<sp/>requirement<sp/>is<sp/>that<sp/>the<sp/>code<sp/>you<sp/>contribute<sp/>adheres<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>restrictions:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/><sp/>Prefix<sp/>members<sp/>variables<sp/>with<sp/>m\_.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/><sp/>Use<sp/>lowerCamelCase<sp/>for<sp/>variables.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/><sp/>Use<sp/>UpperCamelCase<sp/>for<sp/>functions.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/><sp/>Use<sp/>UpperCamelCase<sp/>for<sp/>classes.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/><sp/>Use<sp/>ALL_CAPS<sp/>for<sp/>constants<sp/>and<sp/>macros.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">6.<sp/><sp/>Braces<sp/>always<sp/>start<sp/>on<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>line<sp/>and<sp/>always<sp/>end<sp/>on<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>line.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">7.<sp/><sp/>Spaces,<sp/>not<sp/>tabs.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">8.<sp/><sp/>Avoid<sp/>manual<sp/>memory<sp/>management.<sp/>Use<sp/>unique_ptr<sp/>always.<sp/>This<sp/>helps<sp/>transparent<sp/>hotloading<sp/>later!</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Most<sp/>importantly,<sp/>be<sp/>sure<sp/>never<sp/>to<sp/>manually<sp/>write<sp/>memory<sp/>addresses<sp/>or<sp/>hooks<sp/>yourself.<sp/>These<sp/>must<sp/>ALWAYS<sp/>go<sp/>through<sp/>the<sp/>core<sp/>systems<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>sure<sp/>that<sp/>plugins<sp/>can<sp/>play<sp/>nicely<sp/>together.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
